- Must be compiled using Java 1.8 or higher


Assumptions:

- Students are promoted to the next grade level on the first day after the 
  last day of school (July 1st).

- Kindergarten is only one year and not two.

- Pre-school is any number of years prior to Kindergarten (1 and 100 years 
  are the same).

Build instructions:

- Windows:
    ./gradlew.bat build

- Linux / OSX:
    ./gradlew build

Test instructions:

- Windows:
    ./gradlew.bat test

- Linux / OSX:
    ./gradlew test

Adding your own tests:

- Place your class files containing test methods annotated with the @Test 
  annotation under the path src/test/java. Run them using the same test 
  command.

